N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 18 ยง 483.1 - Voluntary dissolution

State Regulations

An application for approval of the voluntary dissolution
of a not-for-profit corporation shall contain information and data with
reference to: (a) the public need for
such dissolution; (b) the proposed
disposition of the assets of the corporation; and
(c) such other matter, or matters, as may be
deemed to be in the public interest. Notes
